# Bank Account

## Description
A Java application that simulates a bank account with checking and savings balances. Users can deposit, withdraw, and view account information.

## Features
- Deposit money
- Withdraw money
- View checking balance
- View savings balance
- View total balance
- Random 10-digit account number
- Track total accounts created

## Files
- BankAcc.java
- BankTest.java

